{% extends "layouts/standard_content.jinja" %}
{% from "components/card.jinja" import card %}
{% from "components/heading.jinja" import heading %}
{% from "components/contents.jinja" import contents %}
{% from "components/link.jinja" import link %}
{% from "components/list.jinja" import list, list_item %}
{% block mobile_article_title %}
  {% call heading() %}
    Help and Support
  {% endcall %}
{% endblock mobile_article_title %}
{% block desktop_article_title %}
  {% call heading() %}
    Help and Support
  {% endcall %}
{% endblock desktop_article_title %}
{% block article_navigation %}
  {% call contents(title="On this page") %}
    {% call list() %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#getting-started-with-find-case-law") %}
          Getting started with Find Case Law
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#contact-us") %}
          Contact us
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
      {% call list_item() %}
        {% call link(href="#help-us-improve") %}
          Help us improve
        {% endcall %}
      {% endcall %}
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
{% endblock article_navigation %}
{% block article_content %}
  <p>Get help using Find Case Law, report problems and share your feedback to help us improve the service.</p>
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Getting started with Find Case Law
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    New to the service? Visit
    {% call link(href=url("understanding_case_law")) %}
      Understanding Case Law
    {% endcall %}
    to learn about court judgments and how to read them.
  </p>
  <p>
    Ready to search? Our
    {% call link(href=url("search_tips")) %}
      Search tips
    {% endcall %}
    page provides guidance for finding specific cases, including:
  </p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      how to search for case names and citations
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      using keywords effectively
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      filtering by court, date, or judge
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      tips for using advanced search
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  <p>Whether you're a beginner or experienced researcher, our search guidance helps you find what you need quickly.</p>
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Contact us
  {% endcall %}
  <p>If you need direct assistance our team can help with:</p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      technical problems using the service
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      questions about specific judgments
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      reporting errors or issues
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      general enquiries about Find Case Law
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    {% call link(href=url("contact_us")) %}
      Contact us
    {% endcall %}
    to get in touch. We aim to respond to all enquiries promptly.
  </p>
  {% call heading(tag="h2") %}
    Help us improve
  {% endcall %}
  <p>Your feedback and experiences help us make Find Case Law better for everyone.</p>
  <p>Tell us about your experience using Find Case Law through our feedback surveys. Your input helps us:</p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      improve search functionality
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      add features that users need
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      make the service more accessible
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  {% call heading(tag="h3") %}
    Participate in user research
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    We conduct research to understand how people use Find Case Law and what they need. Participating in user research gives you the chance to:
  </p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      shape future features and improvements
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      test new functionality before it launches
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      share your specific needs and challenges
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      help us serve your user community better
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    Visit
    {% call link(href=url("help_and_support")) %}
      Feedback
    {% endcall %}
    to access our surveys and learn about current research opportunities.
  </p>
  {% call heading(tag="h3") %}
    Reporting problems
  {% endcall %}
  <p>
    If you find technical issues, broken links, or errors in judgments, please let us know through our contact form. Include as much detail as possible:
  </p>
  {% call list(variant="bullets") %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      what you were trying to do
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      what went wrong
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      which page or judgment was affected
    {% endcall %}
    {% call list_item() %}
      any error messages you saw
    {% endcall %}
  {% endcall %}
  <p>This helps us investigate and fix problems quickly.</p>
  <p>
    We're constantly improving Find Case Law based on user feedback and changing needs. Check back regularly for new features and expanded coverage.
  </p>
{% endblock article_content %}
